description:
This is a 6 minute workout called 'Technique + Stretch Cool-Down' from the channel Laine Karwoski.
The workout falls under Cool-down/Cool-down.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Rower for this workout.
The workout has a The Reboot Workout and The Masterclass Workout vibe.
The The Reboot Workout vibe means Deep stretch, low stress, total-body refresh. This is especially good for Recovery days, stress relief, post-travel stiffness. The The Masterclass Workout vibe means Technique-driven, focused, skill-building. This is especially good for Those who love precision and mastery in movement..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Prioritize proper form and technique with Laine and Nick, ending your session with a few stretches. 

Max rhythm: 24, Format: Technique...
